风","type":"attack","description":"横向扫击，范围攻击","source_skill":"skill_quan_fa","source_refs":[{"chapter":16,"line_start":134,"line_end":134,"text":"小马道：“因为我打得比人快，也比人准。”"}]},{"id":"tech_fei_shen","name":"飞身","type":"buff","description":"快速移动，躲避攻击","source_skill":"skill_qing_gong","source_refs":[{"chapter":16,"line_start":148,"line_end":148,"text":"这个人凌空跃起，再飘飘落下。"}]},{"id":"tech_tie_qiang","name":"贴墙","type":"defense","description":"轻飘飘贴在墙上，躲避攻击","source_skill":"skill_qing_gong","source_refs":[{"chapter":16,"line_start":266,"line_end":266,"text":"他一拳击出，扫花老人已到了墙上，就象是一张纸一样，轻飘飘地飞了上去，轻飘飘地贴在墙上，看着小马微笑。"}]}],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_lang_shan_zhi_dian","name":"狼山之巅","region":"狼山","one_line":"狼山之王的皇宫所在","source_refs":[{"chapter":16,"line_start":4,"line_end":4,"text":"这条路的尽头，已在山巅。"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"走进去再向左，就可以看见一扇门，敲三次门，就推门进去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":100,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_bu_zhan","text":"朱五太爷？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":114,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_bu_zhan","speaker_name":"卜战","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你来干什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":116,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_bu_zhan","text":"来送礼的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":118,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_bu_zhan","speaker_name":"卜战","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"什么礼？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":120,"line_end":120},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_bu_zhan","text":"一双拳头。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":122,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_bu_zhan","speaker_name":"卜战","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你的拳头？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":124,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_bu_zhan","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_bu_zhan","speaker_name":"卜战","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你这双拳头有什么用？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_bu_zhan","text":"这双拳头会打人，打你要打的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_bu_zhan","speaker_name":"卜战","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"人人的拳头都会打人，我为什么偏偏要你的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_bu_zhan","text":"因为我打得比人快，也比人准。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_bu_zhan","speaker_name":"卜战","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你先打我两拳试试。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":136,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_bu_zhan","text":"好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":138,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_bu_zhan","text":"是你。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":16,"line_start":150,"line_end":150},{"speaker":"char_bu_zhan","speaker_name":"卜战","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你从不在背后打人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":156,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_bu_zhan","text":"嗯。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":158,"line_end":158},{"speaker":"char_bu_zhan","speaker_name":"卜战","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"好，好汉子。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":16,"line_start":160,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_bu_zhan","speaker_name":"卜战","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"敲门五次，推门进去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_wo_ren","text":"朱五太爷？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":168,"line_end":168},{"speaker":"char_wo_ren","speaker_name":"卧人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"不是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":170,"line_end":170},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_wo_ren","text":"你是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":172,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_wo_ren","speaker_name":"卧人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"是个想挨揍的人。","tone":"调侃","chapter":16,"line_start":174,"line_end":174},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_wo_ren","text":"我若想见朱五太爷，就得先接你一顿？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":176,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_wo_ren","speaker_name":"卧人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":178,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_wo_ren","speaker_name":"卧人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"随便你揍我什么地方都行。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":180,"line_end":180},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_wo_ren","text":"好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":182,"line_end":182}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_bu_zhan","name":"卜战","alias":["老狼"],"identity":"狼山高手","faction":"lang_shan","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":5,"one_line":"狼山上的高手，外号老狼","personality":{"traits":["豪爽","直接","威严","老练","幽默"],"speech_style":"豪迈","temperament":"冷静"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":["skill_quan_fa"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[16],"source_refs":[{"chapter":16,"line_start":154,"line_end":154,"text":"这个人不是朱五太爷，是卜战，“老狼”卜战。"}]},{"id":"char_wo_ren","name":"卧人","alias":[],"identity":"狼山守关者","faction":"lang_shan","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":5,"one_line":"狼山第二关守关者","personality":{"traits":["傲慢","自信","直接","轻敌","狡猾"],"speech_style":"淡然","temperament":"傲慢"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[16],"source_refs":[{"chapter":16,"line_start":166,"line_end":166,"text":"屋角有张短榻，短榻上斜卧着一个人，也是背对着门的，却不知是睡是醒。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":300,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"他不好意思见你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":214,"line_end":214},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":216,"line_end":216},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"刚才他还在吹牛，只要你在背后出手，绝对过不了他这一关。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":218,"line_end":220},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你果然没有失信，果然没有在他背后出手。","tone":"微笑","chapter":16,"line_start":222,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"他也没有失信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":226,"line_end":226},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"他想挨揍，现在已挨了揍。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":230,"line_end":230},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"好小子，不但有种，而且还有趣。","tone":"大笑","chapter":16,"line_start":232,"line_end":232},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"我是个好小子，你呢？","tone":"调侃","chapter":16,"line_start":234,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"我只不过是个老头子。","tone":"微笑","chapter":16,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"是老头子？还是老太爷？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":238,"line_end":238},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"老头子通常就是老太爷。","tone":"微笑","chapter":16,"line_start":240,"line_end":240},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"是朱五太爷？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":242,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"怎么样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":272,"line_end":272},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"很好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":274,"line_end":274},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"谁很好？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":276,"line_end":276},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"你很好，我不好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":278,"line_end":278},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你那点不好？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":280,"line_end":280},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"我那么样出手很不好，比起在背后出手已差不了多少。","tone":"无奈","chapter":16,"line_start":282,"line_end":282},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"可是你出手了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":284,"line_end":284},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"因为想试试你。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":286,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你试出了什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":288,"line_end":288},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"我的拳头—向很少打空，今天却已打空了三次。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":290,"line_end":290},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":292,"line_end":292},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"第一次是温良玉，第二次是个见鬼的太阳神使者。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":294,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"那两个人就是狼山上数一数二的高手。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":296,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"但是他们比你还差得多。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":298,"line_end":298},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":300,"line_end":300}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":400,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"自从我上了狼山，你是我遇见的第一高手。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":302,"line_end":302},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"哦。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":304,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"可是我的拳头也不错。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":306,"line_end":306},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"很不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":308,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"而且我会拼命。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":310,"line_end":310},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"我看得出。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":312,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"所以你若肯收下我这双拳头，对你还是很有用。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":314,"line_end":314},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"当然很有用。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"你肯收？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":318,"line_end":318},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"我也很想收下来，只可惜你这双拳并不是送给我的。","tone":"无奈","chapter":16,"line_start":320,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"我是送给朱五太爷的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":324,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":326,"line_end":326},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","text":"你就是朱五太爷，朱五太爷就是你。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"这一次你虽然又看错了人，可是朱五太爷已准备见你。","tone":"微笑","chapter":16,"line_start":334,"line_end":336},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"还有一点你一定要记住。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":340,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"我绝不是山上的第一名高手，在朱五太爷面前，我简直连出手的机会都没有。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":344,"line_end":346},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"所以你在他面前，千万不能放肆，更不能出手，否则必死无疑。","tone":"严肃","chapter":16,"line_start":350,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren","speaker_name":"扫花的老人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"普天之下能见到他真面目的人并不多，所以你进去后无论是死是活，也都可以算不虚此行了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":16,"line_start":354,"line_end":356},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"站住！","tone":"厉声","chapter":16,"line_start":376,"line_end":376},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你已知道我是谁？","tone":"沉声","chapter":16,"line_start":386,"line_end":386},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":388,"line_end":388},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你要见我？","tone":"沉声","chapter":16,"line_start":392,"line_end":392},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":394,"line_end":394},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你姓马？","tone":"沉声","chapter":16,"line_start":396,"line_end":396},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":398,"line_end":398},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"愤怒的小马？","tone":"沉声","chapter":16,"line_start":400,"line_end":400}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","name":"朱五太爷","alias":["狼山之王"],"identity":"狼山之主","faction":"lang_shan","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":8,"one_line":"狼山之王，武功深不可测","personality":{"traits":["威严","神秘","冷酷","智慧","强大"],"speech_style":"沉声","temperament":"威严"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[16],"source_refs":[{"chapter":16,"line_start":392,"line_end":392,"text":"朱五太爷道：“你要见我？”"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":401,"line_end":486,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":402,"line_end":402},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"昔年镖局联营，五犬开花，就是被你和丁喜破了的？","tone":"沉声","chapter":16,"line_start":404,"line_end":406},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":408,"line_end":408},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"好，看坐。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":410,"line_end":410},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"坐下。","tone":"厉声","chapter":16,"line_start":414,"line_end":414},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"五犬开花，气焰不可一世，天下豪杰共厌之，你能击破他们的联营削弱了他们的气势，所以你今日才有坐。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":418,"line_end":420},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"我知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":422,"line_end":422},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"可是有坐未必就有命！","tone":"厉声","chapter":16,"line_start":424,"line_end":424},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"我知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":426,"line_end":426},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"我也知道你并不珍惜你自己这条命","tone":"沉声","chapter":16,"line_start":428,"line_end":428},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你已中了太阳化骨散的毒，最多也只能活到明晨日出时。","tone":"沉声","chapter":16,"line_start":432,"line_end":434},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你的朋友都已陷入绝境，你的情人已落入太阳神使者手里，这次你们同上狼山的人，要想活着下山，已难如登天。","tone":"沉声","chapter":16,"line_start":438,"line_end":440},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"现在你自知已无路可走，所以你才来找我，想用你的一双拳头，换回你们的十条命，","tone":"沉声","chapter":16,"line_start":450,"line_end":450},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你有没有见过只凭在神前烧了一柱香，就能换得终生幸运的人？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":16,"line_start":452,"line_end":454},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"没有见过。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":456,"line_end":456},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"我就是这里的神。","tone":"狂笑","chapter":16,"line_start":458,"line_end":458},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"我的拳头却不是—柱香！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":16,"line_start":460,"line_end":460},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你的拳头是什么？","tone":"沉声","chapter":16,"line_start":462,"line_end":462},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"是个忠心的伙伴，也是件杀人的武器。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":464,"line_end":464},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":466,"line_end":466},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"你并不是真的神，你的力量毕竟有限，能够多一个忠心的伙伴，多一件杀人利器，迟早是有用的。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":468,"line_end":470},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"死人却没有用，十个死人比不止一把快刀，我的拳头还比刀更快。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":472,"line_end":474},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你怎么知道这里没有比你更快的拳头？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":476,"line_end":476},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"全少我还未见过。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":478,"line_end":478},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你想见见？","tone":"疑问","chapter":16,"line_start":480,"line_end":480},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","text":"很想。","tone":"认真","chapter":16,"line_start":482,"line_end":482},{"speaker":"char_zhu_wu_tai_ye","speaker_name":"朱五太爷","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你回头看看。","tone":"陈述","chapter":16,"line_start":484,"line_end":484}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
